<div id="banner">
	<h1>Valenti: &#8220;I know damn well I am infringing.&#8221;</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p><a href="http://cryptome.org/hrcw-hear.htm">House Hearing on Home Recording of Copyrighted Works</a>. On his practice of recording TV shows: &#8220;I am taking somebody else&#8217;s copyrighted material without their consent and I know damn well I am infringing. [&#8230; but it] is not a criminal infringement unless you do it for profit.&#8221;</p>

<p>&#8220;I say to you that the VCR is to the American film producer and the American public as the Boston strangler is to the woman home alone. &#8220;</p>

<p class="posted">posted June 02, 2002 03:44 PM (<a class="category" href="http://www.aaronsw.com/weblog/cat_politics">Politics</a>)  <a href="000310" rel="bookmark">#</a></p>
</div>

